description:
Kat: Sexy, tan, smooth, tiny, hot, energetic, feisty, and she never gives up. She fights to the end; She has the biggest heart and drive of any wrestler on US. If I could take her spirit and put into other wrestlers I would. Kat fights and fights no matter the odds or the opponent. She is a true warrior. Not a very good wrestler but a great competitor, we all want to see her win!

The Punk: Is just that, a bratty skater chick, needs to smile, and is general out for herself. She is street tough and does not take shit. She is coming her to make a name for herself. BTW these two are roommates and best friends, neither one wants to lose to the other.
title: Kat (0-4) The Punk (0-0)
